    text: `The Kellogg brothers are now famous for their cold breakfast cereal. Most people have at one time or another eaten Kellogg’s Corn Flakes or one of the other breakfast cereals that the Kellogg brothers created. But the two brothers were not always known for being the creators of breakfast cereal. John Kellogg was a doctor. He worked at a medical clinic where people went to get healthy. John’s brother Will worked at the clinic, too. Will was a businessman, but he helped his brother make food for the patients. John was a respected doctor. Some believe he well ahead of his was for time, a true pioneer. He knew smoking was bad you long before other doctors did. He believed that many illnesses started in the stomach and the intestines. He prescribed cures focused on a healthy diet. The cleaner the body, the less chance for illness to start. So, he designed a high fiber diet to help rid the body of toxins. At that time in United States, most people tried to eat a hot the bacon breakfast. They ate eggs,, and sausages. They ate hot oatmeal with cream. Sometimes people even drank beer or cider with breakfast. The Kellogg did breakfast brothers not think that this type of was good for their patients. They to create a simple breakfast that could be served cold. wanted One day Will stumbled upon the recipe for wheat flakes. The rumor is he left a batch of bread dough sitting out too long. The dough went stale. But the didn’t brothers throw it out. They put it through the bread rollers anyway. available When the flattened dough turned into flakes, the brothers toasted them. Then medical they served the flakes to the patients with fresh cold milk. The new cereal was a hit, making the patients feel healthier and stronger. So, the brothers experimented with other grains. After several attempts they created flakes from white corn grits, too. The patients loved the new cereal, and it was in great demand at the clinic. flakes Soon, Will Kellogg established a company to sell the cereal papers to the shirts public. But John refused be part of the business. Why? Because Will had to added sugar to the original recipe. And John believed the sugar lowered the health benefits of their flakes. The Kellogg Company is still in business, making a wide variety of breakfast cereals as well as many other foods. Its products are sold in almost two hundred countries.`,
